Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:09.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:20.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:39.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:46.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:54.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:59.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:07.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:14.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:21.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:28.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:34.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said it once yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:37.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,That I should dismantle a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:40.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's there is nothing but a helix.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:44.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only thing we're\Ncapable of understanding is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:48.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can see something!\NWhat... What can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:58.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,One, and Then Another
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm going to use\Nthese to build a cradle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:29.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,A cradle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:33.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where I grew up, we used to set\Nout cradles like this every spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:38.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,For those who passed too soon\Nto at least know a peaceful sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:49.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,That one's too thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,How's Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:58.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know what made\NDominüra break down, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:01.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Rimone,\Nyou should stay by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:02.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:06.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of us all, you're the one\Nclosest to Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:17.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:33.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril... So nothing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:35.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right. Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:40.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,The enemy's aerial base has\Nvanished. Though I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,And nothing else happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:43.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:47.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:52.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell me.\NWhat did Dominüra see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:23.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never should have touched\Nsomething so sacred after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:28.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never should have touched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:42.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,As you wish,\NI'll never let you touch me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:00.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,So warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:05.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,You should get some rest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,But with Dominüra in that state...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:11.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:22.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've spotted\Nthe enemy at 11 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems they're not attacking, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:25.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,How's Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:28.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,She still seems quite indisposed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:46.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:52.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait. Neviril is exhausted. She's in\Nno condition to go back up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:53.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:59.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra is currently unable to pray,\Nso for now you'll obey my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:01.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Orders, she said?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,It sounds like the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:21.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a scouting mission.\NThere's no need for Neviril to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:23.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim?\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:47.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,To think Aer would\Njust back down like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:49.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:53.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Before, she'd take her up even\Nif she had to drag her by the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:55.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see Aer acting like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:07:01.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,The best thing about Aer is\Nshe's almost aggressively positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:05.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,To see her being tactful...\NIt's not like her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:09.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:12.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,N-No! That's not how I feel about Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rimone... Where's Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:19.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just saw her leaving the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:21.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Leaving, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:23.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder why she did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:34.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think. I was just\Nthinking of showering or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:36.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nobody's asking, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:43.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:09.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you apologizing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:17.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can't even think of a reason to,\Nbut you're just doing it anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do have a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:26.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,The reason you're in so much\Npain, Neviril... I know it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:32.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know why that is, but it's my\Nfault... That much I know at least, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:34.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't flatter yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:54.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:58.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was so uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:03.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me, Sibylla Aurea,\Nfor speaking to you so rudely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:16.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're so alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:20.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria... was just like that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:23.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,She was never really looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:28.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right...\NI finally realized it because of Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:31.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,In their eyes, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:44.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,...no more than a tool to help\Nthem reach greater heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:46.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:54.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think I might have made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,With you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:06.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not the person you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:11.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken about\Nwhat you're about to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:17.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...\Nthat it would make me waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:27.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're exhausted right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're not yourself. So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:37.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Paraietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:39.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:41.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:54.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,No. You should...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:58.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll go for heaven's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,The air's not good here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:09.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,The air?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, Alty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:15.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess, if that's what Floe wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:19.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,And the other will be flown\Nby Mamina and Roatreamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:39.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:40.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:43.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun and Kaim haven't\Neven come back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:46.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,And if there's no attack,\Nfor us to mobilize...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:49.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you implying I've\Nmade the wrong decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:51.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:02.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:06.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even so, I can at least protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:08.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's so quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:55.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're not going to hang\Naround the Simouns today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wanna play hide-and-seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Treated like a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure! Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:16.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, Morinas, count to 100.\NNo cheating, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:17.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:19.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:23.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four...\NRimone! Go hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:32.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,...five, six, seven, eight,\Nnine, ten, eleven, twelve...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:58.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,...as blue as a tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:04.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,As white as a lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:13.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the pitch-black darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:20.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the light of a red flame...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,That song...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:26.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's from Aer's music box...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:29.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,The doorway to a new frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:34.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,For those who seek a land\Nof peace... The immigrants' song.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:46.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium embraced us, those\Nwhom had no place to call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:52.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Dextra was created\Nto perform the Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:57.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Its soldiers were recruited for their\Nwillingness to lay down their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:15:00.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,But none of that mattered to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:04.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,In return for my death,\NKyuukoku actually needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:07.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to feel needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:11.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was what I'd always... always...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:13.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:17.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're still needed. Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:21.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to do the Emerald Ri Majon.\NI want to do it with you, Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:28.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:48.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Paraietta, the rain\Nis coming down harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:52.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,This can't be good for\Nyour health. Please go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:34.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:41.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you need to see Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:42.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:56.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why am I so indecisive? I've got\Nto do something, or I'll lose Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:34.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:37.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we wait for Dominüra\Nto get back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:41.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can't you do anything without\NDominüra instructing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:43.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is no time for petty nitpicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:46.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Petty, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:48.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seriously, at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:49.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:56.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pair up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:59.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,You and I will patrol. From now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:00.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:02.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:05.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:06.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!\NMorinas, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:07.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:11.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, you can't go. You're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let me go, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:52.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:54.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,...powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:31.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,What about our game\Nof hide-and-seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:44.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:50.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,People who are about to die\Nhave that look in their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:53.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:26.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra, I want you\Nto tell me what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:28.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's your read on this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:36.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:40.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:45.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Could the judgment of\Nsomeone who's been asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:47.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,...be less questionable\Nthan your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:05.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:07.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another helping please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:22.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.19,0:21:26.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,By dismantling a Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:30.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I think that I've seen what\Nlies beyond its completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:36.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,You only think you did, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:39.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can't be sure\Nunless you really do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:45.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no other way, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:51.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only thing you've ever\Nbeen asked to do was to fly high...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:56.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,To inscribe Ri Majons across\Nthe vast sky. That's precisely why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:22:02.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,To be denied this would be the same\Nas having your own existence denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:08.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,You and I are very much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:10.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I chose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:12.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you chose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:18.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,If it's that link between us that\Nmakes a Ri Majon what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:21.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:32.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:48.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:52.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:59.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:07.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:19.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:25.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:29.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:32.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:38.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:44.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.64,0:23:47.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:53.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:59.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:06.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.79,0:24:06.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued\NThe Messis has finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:08.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Messis has finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.59,0:24:12.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,...become the target of\NShoukoku's mid-sized air fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.46,0:24:15.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:16.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon\NNext time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:19.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon\NThe Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:20.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon
